text: That's Not What I Heard is the debut studio album by the American garage rock band Gossip (under their old name The Gossip), it was released on January 23, 2001. ==Track listing== # "Swing Low" – 1:18 # "Got All This Waiting" – 1:47 # "Bones" – 2:09 # "Sweet Baby" – 1:41 # "Tuff Luv" – 1:14 # "Got Body If You Want It" – 2:02 # "Where the Girls Are" – 1:44 # "Bring It On" – 2:26 # "Heartbeats" – 1:44 # "Catfight" – 1:15 # "Jailbreak" – 1:23 # "Southern Comfort" – 1:07 # "And You Know..." – 1:49 # "Hott Date" – 2:16 ==Personnel== * Beth Ditto – vocals, piano * Brace Paine – guitar, bass guitar * Kathy Mendonça – drums == References == Category:2001 debut albums Category:Gossip (band) albums Category:Kill Rock Stars albums
title: That's Not What I Heard
